Get out of Jixing Abyss!

150
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:05,720
-Get out of Jixing Abyss!
-Get out of Jixing Abyss!

151
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:09,360
-Get out of Jixing Abyss!
-Get out of Jixing Abyss!

152
