222
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:16,560
-Jixing Abyss!
-Jixing Abyss!

223
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:20,040
-Jixing Abyss!
-Jixing Abyss!

224
00:12:43,920 --> 00:12:45,000
Get out.

