234
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:33,040
Chao Yuan, forget her.

235
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:40,440
Forget her,

236
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:44,080
and you will be the one

237
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:46,760
most likely to rule
Zhushui Spiritual State.

238
